Jimmy the Chisel is the apprentice of Aggie the witch. He was thrown in the jail cell of the H.A.M. Hideout. During the Death to the Dorgeshuun quest he says what happens to Zanik after the player is thrown in jail. During One Small Favour, Aggie's favour is to find Jimmy in exchange for being a character witness for Brian's friend. Once found, Johanhus Ulsbrecht will offer to let Jimmy go for "a month's supply of chickens" from Fred the Farmer.
